The potential of the AfCFTA to address more than trade related issues cannot be overstated. Better integrated economies through the implementation of the Agreement will enable the levels of economies of scale and investment necessary to build capacities for the continent to produce more of what it consumes.



if (shouldRenderAd(false)) {
